title: ‘SNL’ Star Pete Davidson Won’t Be on Blue Origin’s Next Flight After All
sub_head: New launch date didn’t work with comedian’s schedule
body:
Pete Davidson won’t be blasting into space next week after all.
Blue Origin, the company offering the 11-minute flight to him free, moved the takeoff date from March 23 to March 29, making the “Saturday Night Live” star unable to attend.
